item.title: Trip
item.description: 2023: North Rustico to Cap Egmont, 9 days, 200 nautical miles or 370 km. 2024: Cap Egmont to North Rustico, hopefully 5-6 days at most, weather permitting, roughly 100 nautical miles left.
